This paper discusses a machine learning approach (S3VM) and proposes a method to improve its performance through the selection of unlabeled instances. This falls under the category of "Machine Learning" (cs.LG) and "Artificial Intelligence" (cs.AI). The paper also mentions experiments on data sets, which suggests a focus on "Computer Vision" (cs.CV) and "Data Mining" (cs.DM). Additionally, the use of clustering techniques for instance selection may also relate to "Computational Linguistics" (cs.CL).
